title: Case Was Received
body: On March 3, 2021, we received your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190122000, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
